Saurin karuwar yawan kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila, daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020
Yawan kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) yana nuna irin wannan yanayin a cikin ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila yana tabbatar da cewa, yayin da yake a wani mataki daban-daban dangane da ƙasar, annobar COVID-19 tana ci gaba cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Dangane da kwarewar Italiya, ƙasashe, asibitoci da sassan kulawa da hankali ya kamata su ƙara shirye-shiryen su don karuwar marasa lafiya da COVID-19 waɗanda za su buƙaci kula da lafiya, musamman kulawa mai tsanani.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an ba da rahoton tarin cututtukan ciwon huhu na rashin sani a Wuhan, Lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga Janairun 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cututtuka ta China ta ba da rahoton cewa mai haifar da cutar shine sabon coronavirus wanda yanzu ake kira da cutar coronavirus mai tsanani mai tsanani 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ke haifar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 an kira ta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Shaida har zuwa yau ita ce kusan kashi 80% na mutanen da ke da COVID-19 suna da cutar mai sauƙi, watau kamuwa da cutar numfashi tare da ko ba tare da ciwon huhu ba, kuma yawancin waɗannan suna murmurewa.
A cikin kusan kashi 14% na lokuta, COVID-19 ya zama mummunan cuta wanda ke buƙatar asibiti yayin da sauran kashi 6% na lokuta ke fuskantar mummunan cuta wanda ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Mutuwar marasa lafiya da aka kwantar a asibiti saboda COVID-19 kusan 4%.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun kimanta yanayin haɗuwa da cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU / EEA) da United Kingdom (UK) kuma mun kwatanta su da na lardin Hubei, China.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin masu cutar COVID-19 a yanzu a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya da na Italiya a lokacin 31 ga Janairu15 ga Maris 2020.
Cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya kara yaduwa a yankuna kuma halin da annobar COVID-19 ke ciki a sauran duniya a halin yanzu yana bin wannan ƙasar.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin fitowar 5 ga Maris na Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. sun ba da rahoton farkon yanayin COVID-19 da aka tabbatar a Turai bisa ga ma'anar shari'ar WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, Faransa ta ba da rahoton farkon lokuta uku da aka tabbatar a ranar 24 ga Janairu 2020 a cikin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, Lardin Hubei, China.
Ya zuwa ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano shari'o'in COVID-19 a duk ƙasashe 30 na EU/EEA da United Kingdom (UK), inda tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019 da wannan ranar, an ba da rahoton shari'o'i 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727, tare da shari'o'i 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 daga Italiya kadai.
Samun jimlar adadin da kuma yawan adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19
A Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), ana sabunta adadin masu cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a duniya, wanda aka samo daga tushen hukuma kawai kamar su ma'aikatar lafiya ta ƙasashe, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki da WHO, kowace rana da ƙarfe 8:00 na safe.
An yi amfani da waɗannan bayanan don kimanta yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya, da kuma kwatanta su da na Italiya.
A matsayin mai wakiltar yaduwar masu cutar COVID-19, mun lissafa yawan adadin masu cutar COVID-19 na kwanaki 14, don haka muna la'akari da yanayin COVID-19, a kowace EU / EEA da Burtaniya, a lokacin 1 ga Janairu  15 ga Maris 2020.
Mun kuma gabatar da jimlar adadin masu cutar da aka sanar a kowace ƙasa a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da ƙarfe 8:00 na safe idan aka kwatanta da na Italiya don lokacin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Hanyoyin COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK
Hanyoyin da aka samu na kwanaki 14 na raguwar yawan masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK gabaɗaya sun bi na lardin Hubei (China) (Hoto na 1).
Ga EU/EEA da UK gabaɗaya, yawan kamuwa da COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a kusan 21 ga Fabrairu sannan ya ƙaru sosai a kusan 28 ga Fabrairu 2020 (Sarin bayani).
Wannan galibi ya samo asali ne daga saurin karuwar adadin masu cutar daga Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU / EEA da Burtaniya sun nuna irin wannan karuwar yanayin haɗuwa da cutar COVID-19 (Sarin bayani).
Hoto na 2 ya nuna yawan adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19, a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya idan aka kwatanta da na Italiya na tsawon 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Ya jaddada cewa, a ranar 15 ga Maris da karfe 8:00 na safe, wasu ƙasashe 15 na EU/EEA da Burtaniya sun riga sun ba da rahoton jimlar adadin shari'o'in da za a iya kwatanta da na Italiya makonni 3 da suka gabata ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa yawan masu kamuwa da COVID-19 da aka sanar suna karuwa cikin sauri a EU/EEA da UK.
Hanyoyin da aka lura a cikin yawan kamuwa da COVID-19 ya nuna cewa annobar tana ci gaba da saurin daidaitawa a duk ƙasashe.
Wannan duk da cewa ƙasashe suna cikin matakai daban-daban, bambance-bambance a cikin martani na lafiyar jama'a na ƙasa, kuma wataƙila ma'anar shari'ar daban-daban a cikin ƙasashe da ladabi daban-daban don zaɓar marasa lafiya waɗanda dole ne a gwada su don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da gwajin kamawa.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa na Italiya sun bayyana halin da kusan kashi 10% na marasa lafiya da ke da COVID-19 ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ba da rahoton cewa asibitoci da sassan kulawa mai tsanani a waɗannan yankuna sun riga sun kai iyakar ƙarfin su.
Bayanai kan shigar da masu cutar COVID-19 asibiti da/ko sashin kulawa mai tsanani a halin yanzu ana samun su a matakin EU/EEA don kashi 6% da 1% na masu cutar, bi da bi (ba a nuna bayanai ba).
Duk da haka, ya kamata a tattara su ta hanyar da ta dace don haɓaka bayanan sa ido na yanzu waɗanda ke mai da hankali kan yawan adadin da aka ruwaito da yawan mutuwar.
Wani bincike da aka gudanar a 201011 ya nuna bambancin da ke tsakanin wuraren kula da marasa lafiya a Turai, daga 29.2 a Jamus zuwa 4.2 a kowace 100,000 a Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe na iya samun ƙarin ko ƙasa da albarkatu fiye da Italiya (12.5 gadaje masu kulawa da kulawa da matsakaici ga kowane mazauna 100,000 a 201011).
Ana ba da yanayin samfurin da ya shafi ƙoshin lafiyar lafiya, tare da kimantawa ga kowace ƙasa ta EU / EEA da Burtaniya na yawan cututtukan COVID-19 da aka kwantar a asibiti da ke da alaƙa da haɗarin 90% na wucewa ƙarfin gadajen kulawa mai tsanani a cikin sabuntawa na shida na kimanta haɗarin ECDC mai sauri akan COVID-19.
Tun da har yanzu an tattara masu cutar a wasu yankuna a cikin EU/EEA da Birtaniya, kuma asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa da hankali suna ba da sabis ga yawan mutanen yankin da aka ƙayyade, ya kamata a ba da bayanai game da lokuta da gadaje masu kulawa da hankali a cikin Nomenclature of territorial units for statistics 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwarewar Italiya da abubuwan da ke faruwa a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana ci gaba cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya.
Don haka, ƙasashe, asibitoci da sassan kulawa da hankali ya kamata su shirya kansu don yanayin ci gaba da watsawa na al'umma na SARS-CoV-2 da ƙaruwar yawan marasa lafiya da COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kula da lafiya, musamman kulawa mai tsanani, kamar wanda ke faruwa a yankunan da cutar ta shafa na Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin sabon kimanta haɗarin ECDC, hanzari, mai saurin aiki da cikakkiyar hanya yana da mahimmanci don jinkirta yaduwar SARS-COV-2, tare da sauyawa daga hanyar hanawa zuwa hanyar ragewa, saboda saurin karuwar adadin shari'o'in da ake tsammani na iya ba masu yanke shawara da asibitoci isasshen lokaci don fahimta, karɓa da daidaita amsar su daidai idan ba a aiwatar da su ba a gaba.
Har ila yau, kimantawar haɗarin cikin sauri ta lissafa matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a don rage tasirin annobar.
Akwai ɗan gajeren lokaci na dama wanda ƙasashe ke da damar ƙara haɓaka ƙoƙarin sarrafa su don rage saurin yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da rage matsin lamba kan kiwon lafiya.
Idan ba haka ba, da alama tsarin kiwon lafiya na sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA za su fuskanci karuwar marasa lafiya da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa ko makonni.
Cutar Coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wadda ta haifar da cutar coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), ta kashe mutane sama da 3,000 kuma ta kamu da sama da 80,000 a China da sauran wurare a duniya, wanda hakan ya haifar da bala'i ga mutane.
Kamar kwayar cutar ta homologous, SARS-CoV, wacce ta haifar da SARS a cikin dubban mutane a 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya yaduwa daga jemage kuma yana haifar da irin wannan alamun ta hanyar irin wannan tsari.
Koyaya, COVID-19 yana da ƙananan tsanani da mutuwa fiye da SARS amma yana da yawa fiye da yaduwa kuma yana shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa da maza fiye da mata.
Domin yawan littattafan da ake wallafawa game da wannan cuta, wannan talifin yana ƙoƙari ya ba da cikakken bayani game da wannan cuta da ake yi a yau.
Za mu tattauna abubuwa na asali game da cututtukan cututtuka, cututtukan cututtuka, cututtukan cututtuka, ganewar asali, magani, tsinkaya, da kuma rigakafin cutar.
