Bikin bazara a ranar 25 ga Janairun 2020 ya zama abin tunawa da ba a taɓa mantawa da shi ba ga duk Sinawa waɗanda aka aririce su su zauna a gida duk lokacin hutu da kuma makonni da yawa bayan haka saboda barkewar sabon cutar kwayar cuta.
Kwayar cutar tana da kama da kwayar cutar coronavirus (CoV) wacce ta haifar da barkewar cutar cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani (SARS) a cikin 2003; don haka, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta kira ta SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, kuma an kira cutar da ke tattare da ita Cutar CoV-19 (COVID-19).
Cutar ta fara ne a Wuhan, China, kuma ta bazu cikin sauri a duk faɗin ƙasar da kuma kusan wasu 50 a duk faɗin duniya.
Ya zuwa ranar 2 ga Maris, 2020, kwayar cutar ta haifar da sama da mutane 80,000 da aka tabbatar da cutar COVID-19, tare da sama da marasa lafiya 40,000 da aka sallama kuma sama da marasa lafiya 3,000 da suka mutu.
