Zazzabi ne sau da yawa babban kuma farkon alamun COVID-19, wanda zai iya kasancewa ba tare da wata alama ba ko wasu alamun kamar bushewa tari, numfashi, ciwon tsoka, maƙarƙashiya, ciwon kai, ciwon makogwaro, rhinorrhea, ciwon kirji, zawo, tashin zuciya, da amai.
