Fitowar SARS-CoV-2 a tsakiyar China a ƙarshen 2019 ya sake sanya CoVs cikin hasken haske kuma ya ba mu mamaki da yawan yaduwar sa amma rage cutar idan aka kwatanta da 'yar'uwarsa SARS-CoV.
Cutar HCoV cuta ce ta dabbobi kuma fahimtar asalin dabbobi na HCoVs zai taimaka mana sosai.
Yawancin HCoVs sun samo asali ne daga jemage inda ba su da cutar.
Hakanan an san masu karɓar bakunan ajiyar matsakaici na wasu HCoVs.
Gano dabbobi masu karɓar baƙi yana da tasiri kai tsaye kan rigakafin cututtukan ɗan adam.
Binciken hulɗar CoV-mai masauki a cikin dabbobi na iya samun mahimman bayanai game da cutar CoV a cikin mutane.
A cikin wannan bita, muna gabatar da bayyani game da ilimin da ake da shi game da HCoVs bakwai, tare da mai da hankali kan tarihin gano su da asalin su na dabbobi da watsawa tsakanin jinsuna.
Abu mai mahimmanci, muna kwatanta da bambancin HCoVs daban-daban daga mahangar juyin halittar kwayar cutar da sake haɗuwa da kwayoyin halitta.
An tattauna cutar CoV ta yanzu ta 2019 (COVID-19) a cikin wannan mahallin.
Bugu da kari, ana kuma jaddada bukatun don sauya mai masaukin da ya yi nasara da kuma tasirin juyin halittar kwayar cutar akan tsananin cutar.
Coronaviruses (CoVs) suna cikin dangin Coronaviridae, wanda ya ƙunshi rukuni na murfin, mai jin daɗi, ƙwayoyin RNA guda ɗaya.
Wadannan ƙwayoyin cuta da ke ɗauke da mafi girman kwayoyin halitta na kilobases 26 zuwa 32 a tsakanin ƙwayoyin cuta na RNA an kira su CoVs saboda siffarsu kamar kambi a ƙarƙashin madubin lantarki.
A tsarin, CoVs suna da kwayoyin halittar da ba a rarraba su ba waɗanda ke da tsari iri ɗaya.
Kimanin kashi biyu bisa uku na kwayoyin halitta sun ƙunshi manyan manyan manyan manyan manyan manyan manyan (ORF1a da ORF1b), waɗanda aka fassara zuwa pp1a da pp1ab replicase polyproteins.
Ana ci gaba da sarrafa polyproteins don samar da sunadarai 16 marasa tsari, wanda aka sanya nsp1 ~ 16.
Sauran ɓangaren kwayoyin halitta yana ƙunshe da ORFs don sunadarai masu tsari, ciki har da ƙwanƙwasa (S), murfi (E), membrane (M) da nucleoprotein (N).
Hakanan ana tsara wasu furotin masu amfani da layi daban-daban ta hanyar layi daban-daban na CoVs.
Dangane da bambanci a cikin jerin sunadarai, ana rarraba CoVs zuwa jinsi huɗu (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV da delta-CoV), daga cikinsu jinsunan beta-CoV suna ƙunshe da yawancin HCoVs kuma an raba su zuwa zuriya huɗu (A, B, C da D).
Shaidar Phylogenetic ta nuna cewa jemage da rodents suna aiki a matsayin tushen kwayoyin halitta na yawancin alpha-CoVs da beta-CoVs, yayin da tsuntsaye sune babban ma'ajiyar gamma-CoVs da delta-CoVs.
A cikin dubban shekaru, CoVs koyaushe suna ƙetare shingen jinsuna kuma wasu sun fito a matsayin mahimman ƙwayoyin cuta na ɗan adam.
Zuwa yau, an san CoVs guda bakwai na mutum (HCoVs).
Daga cikin su HCoV-229E da HCoV-NL63 sune alpha-CoVs.
Sauran beta-CoVs guda biyar sun haɗa da HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, coronavirus mai ciwon numfashi mai tsanani (SARS-CoV), coronavirus na ciwon numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS-CoV) da SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 da HCoV-NL63 yawanci suna haifar da alamun rashin lafiya, kamar sanyi da / ko zawo.
Sabanin haka, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV da sabon SARS-CoV-2 da aka gano suna da cutar cuta sosai, suna haifar da mummunar kamuwa da cutar ƙananan hanyoyin numfashi a cikin marasa lafiya da yawa tare da mafi girman damar haɓaka cutar rashin lafiyar numfashi (ARDS) da bayyanar cututtuka.
An ware HCoV-229E na farko, B814, daga ɓoyayyen hanci na marasa lafiya da sanyi a tsakiyar shekarun 1960.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, an sami ƙarin ilimi ta hanyar zurfin karatu kan HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43, dukansu suna haifar da alamun cutar kai tsaye.
A zahiri, ra'ayin da aka yarda da shi cewa kamuwa da cutar HCoVs gabaɗaya ba shi da lahani har zuwa barkewar SARS.
Cutar SARS da ta faru a 2003 tana daya daga cikin mafi muni a tarihin yanzu, ta kamu da mutane sama da 8,000 tare da mutuwar mutum kusan 10%.
Shekaru goma bayan haka, barkewar cutar cututtukan numfashi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS) ta haifar da barkewar annoba a cikin yankin Larabawa tare da yaduwar bazuwar zuwa sauran duniya.
Sabuwar HCoV ta 2019 (2019-nCoV), wacce daga baya aka sake masa suna SARS-CoV-2, ita ce sanadin yaduwar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wacce ta kashe mutane sama da 3,120 kuma ta kamu da mutane sama da 91,000 har zuwa 3 ga Maris, 2020.
An yi kararrawa kuma dole ne duniya ta shirya don annobar SARS-CoV-2 mai zuwa.
Dukkanin HCoVs bakwai suna da asalin dabbobi daga jemage, beraye ko dabbobin gida.
Hanyoyi da yawa na shaida suna tallafawa asalin juyin halitta na duk HCoVs daga bats, inda ƙwayoyin cuta suka dace da kyau kuma ba su da cutar amma suna nuna bambancin kwayoyin halitta.
Cutar COVID-19 ta haifar da manyan kalubale na kiwon lafiya, kimiyya, zamantakewa da ɗabi'a ga China da duniya.
Binciken asalin HCoVs na dabbobi yana ba da tsarin don fahimtar tarihin halitta, ƙarfin motsawa da abubuwan ƙuntatawa na tsalle-tsalle na jinsuna.
Wannan kuma na iya jagorantar ko sauƙaƙa binciken mai tanadin, matsakaici da haɓaka mai karɓar dabbobi na SARS-CoV-2, tare da mahimman tasiri wajen hana yaduwar gaba.
A cikin wannan bita mun gabatar da bayyani game da asalin zoonotic, watsawa tsakanin jinsuna da kuma cutar ta HCoVs.
Musamman, muna haskakawa da tattauna batun gama gari cewa ƙwayoyin cuta na iyaye na HCoVs yawanci ba su da cutar a cikin masu riƙe da su na halitta amma sun zama masu cutar bayan watsawa tsakanin nau'ikan zuwa sabon mai masaukin.
Mun kuma sake nazarin yanayin juyin HCoV wanda yawan karuwar yaduwar cutar sau da yawa yana zuwa tare da raguwar cutar.
Hakanan ana tattauna sakamakon barkewar cutar SARS-CoV-2 a wannan mahallin.
An san CoVs na dabbobi tun daga ƙarshen 1930s.
Kafin a fara ware HCoV-229E nau'in B814 daga ɓoyayyen hanci na marasa lafiya waɗanda suka kamu da sanyi, an ware CoVs daban-daban a cikin dabbobi daban-daban da ke fama da cutar, gami da turkey, linzamin kwamfuta, saniya, alade, cat da kare.
A cikin shekarun da suka gabata, an gano HCoVs bakwai.
Takaitaccen tarihin gano HCoV a cikin tsari na lokaci (Table 1) zai zama mai ba da bayani da kuma koyarwa.
An ware nau'in HCoV-229E na farko daga hanyoyin numfashi na marasa lafiya da ke fama da kamuwa da cutar na sama a cikin shekara ta 1966, kuma daga baya an daidaita shi don girma a cikin layin ƙwayoyin WI-38.
Marasa lafiya da ke dauke da HCoV-229E sun nuna alamun sanyi na yau da kullun, gami da ciwon kai, hancin, rashin lafiya da ciwon makogwaro, tare da zazzabi da tari da aka gani a cikin kashi 10 ~ 20%.
Daga baya a cikin 1967, an ware HCoV-OC43 daga al'adun gabobin jiki da kuma wucewa ta jere a cikin kwakwalwar berayen shayarwa.
Abubuwan asibiti na kamuwa da cutar HCoV-OC43 suna kama da waɗanda HCoV-229E ke haifarwa, waɗanda alamun cututtuka ba za a iya rarrabe su da kamuwa da wasu cututtukan cututtukan numfashi kamar ƙwayoyin cuta na mura A da rhinoviruses ba.
Dukansu HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43 suna rarraba a duniya, kuma galibi ana watsa su ne a lokacin hunturu a cikin yanayin zafi.
Gabaɗaya, lokacin ɓoye waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta biyu bai kai mako ɗaya ba, sannan kuma kusan makonni 2 na rashin lafiya.
Dangane da binciken da aka yi kan masu sa kai, mutane masu lafiya da ke dauke da cutar HCoV-229E sun kamu da cutar sanyi mai sauƙi.
Kawai wasu marasa lafiya marasa lafiya sun nuna mummunan kamuwa da ƙananan cututtukan numfashi.
SARS, wanda kuma aka sani da atypical pneumonia, shine farkon annobar da HCoV ta haifar a tarihin ɗan adam kuma mai haifar da cutar shine SARS-CoV, HCoV na uku da aka gano.
Ana iya gano farkon cutar SARS a ƙarshen 2002 a lardin Guangdong na China.
Cutar ta SARS ta haifar da rahotanni 8,096 da suka shafi mutuwar 774, wanda ya bazu a ƙasashe da nahiyoyi da yawa.
Baya ga masu yaduwar cutar, an kiyasta cewa kowace shari'a na iya haifar da kusan shari'o'i biyu na biyu, tare da lokacin kwantar da hankali na kwanaki 4 zuwa 7 kuma mafi girman nauyin kwayar cutar yana bayyana a rana ta 10 na cutar.
Marasa lafiya da ke dauke da SARS-CoV da farko suna da ciwon jijiyoyin jiki, ciwon kai, zazzabi, rashin lafiya da sanyi, sannan kuma rashin numfashi, tari da wahalar numfashi a matsayin alamun bayyanar cututtuka.
Lymphopenia, gwajin aikin hanta da haɓaka creatine kinase sune abubuwan da suka faru na dakin gwaje-gwaje na SARS.
Hakanan ana lura da lalacewar alveolar mai yaduwa, yaduwar ƙwayoyin epithelial da ƙaruwar macrophages a cikin marasa lafiya na SARS.
Kimanin kashi 20-30% na marasa lafiya suna buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani da iska mai iska.
Baya ga ƙananan hanyoyin numfashi, gabobin da yawa ciki har da na hanji, hanta da koda suma suna iya kamuwa da cutar a cikin waɗannan mawuyacin yanayi, yawanci tare da guguwar cytokine, wanda zai iya zama mai kisa musamman a cikin marasa lafiya marasa lafiya.
An fara ware kwayar cutar daga kwayar cutar huhu ta wani dangin mai cutar wanda ya yi tafiya zuwa Hong Kong daga Guangzhou.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, an sadaukar da ƙoƙari sosai don binciken HCoV.
An ware HCoV-NL63 daga yaro ɗan wata 7 daga Netherlands a ƙarshen 2004.
Da farko an gano cewa ya zama ruwan dare a cikin yara ƙanana, tsofaffi da marasa lafiya masu fama da cututtukan numfashi.
Bayyanawar coryza, conjunctivitis, zazzabi, da bronchiolitis na kowa ne a cikin cutar da HCoV-NL63 ke haifarwa.
Wani binciken mai zaman kansa ya bayyana ware kwayar cutar iri ɗaya daga samfurin hanci daga yaro ɗan wata 8 da ke fama da ciwon huhu a Netherlands.
Ko da yake an gano shi ne a ƙasar Netherlands, amma a zahiri an rarraba shi a dukan duniya.
An kiyasta cewa HCoV-NL63 yana da kusan kashi 4.7% na cututtukan numfashi na yau da kullun, kuma yawan cutarsa yana faruwa a farkon bazara, bazara da hunturu.
