Wani shawarwari na gaba yana goyon bayan sake haɗuwa tsakanin beta-CoV mai alaƙa da SARS-CoV-2 da kuma RaTG13 a cikin nau'in dabba na uku.
A matsayin ƙarfin motsawa a cikin juyin halitta, sake haɗuwa yana yaduwa tsakanin beta-CoVs.
Har yanzu ba a yanke hukunci kan asalin cutar SARS-CoV-2 ba.
Baya ga HCoVs masu cutarwa sosai, an kuma yi nazarin asalin HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-NL63 da HCoV-HKU1.
Shaidar phylogenetic ta nuna cewa duka HCoV-NL63 da HCoV-229E na iya samo asali ne daga CoVs na bat, yayin da aka sami ƙwayoyin cuta na iyaye na HCoV-OC43 da HCoV-HKU1 a cikin rodents.
An bayar da rahoton cewa CoV na bera da ake kira ARCoV.2 (Appalachian Ridge CoV) da aka gano a cikin dan damisa mai launin fata na Arewacin Amurka ya nuna alaƙar da ke tsakanin HCoV-NL63.
A gefe guda, HCoV-229E yana da alaƙa da wata ƙwayar CoV ta bat, da ake kira Hipposideros / GhanaKwam/19/2008, wanda aka gano a Ghana, yayin da ake zargin camellida a matsayin mai watsa shiri na tsakiya.
Don tsabta, ilimin yanzu game da asalin dabbobi na sanannun HCoVs an taƙaita su a cikin Hoto 1 da Tebur 2.
Binciken phylogenetic ya samar da hujja game da abubuwan watsawa tsakanin jinsuna na HCoVs a cikin tarihi.
Lokacin da HCoV-OC43 ya ƙetare nau'in don ya kamu da mutane daga dabbobin gida a kusa da 1890, an yi rikodin cutar kamuwa da cutar numfashi.
Tarihin watsawa tsakanin jinsuna na HCoV-229E bai bayyana sosai ba.
An gano bat alpha-CoVs da ke da alaƙa da HCoV-229E.
Tsakanin su akwai alpha-CoV na alpaca.
Akwai shaidu da dama da ke nuna cewa kwayar cutar tana yaduwa daga kuraje zuwa mutane kai tsaye.
Na farko, mutane amma ba alpacas ba na iya hulɗa da bat a cikin wani yanki na muhalli.
Maimakon haka, mutane suna da dangantaka ta kusa da alpacas.
Na biyu, alpha-CoVs na bera masu alaƙa da HCoV-229E sun bambanta kuma ba su da cutar a cikin bera, yayin da alpaca alpha-CoV ya haifar da barkewar cutar numfashi a cikin dabbobi masu kamuwa da cuta.
A ƙarshe, ba a sami alpaca alpha-CoV a cikin dabbobin daji ba.
Don haka, ba za a iya cire yiwuwar alpacas su sami alpha-CoV mai alaƙa da HCoV-229E daga mutane ba.
A zahiri, jemage sune tushen kai tsaye na ƙwayoyin cuta masu cutar ɗan adam ciki har da ƙwayar cutar hauka, ƙwayar cutar Ebola, ƙwayar Nipah da ƙwayar cutar Hendra.
Saboda haka ba abin mamaki bane cewa jemage na iya watsa HCoV-229E kai tsaye ga mutane.
A madadin haka, yayin da bat alpha-CoVs ke aiki a matsayin tarin kwayoyin halittar HCoV-229E, alpacas da raƙuma dromedary na iya zama masu watsawa na tsaka-tsaki waɗanda ke watsa ƙwayoyin cuta ga mutane, daidai kamar yadda yake a cikin yanayin MERS-CoV.
MERS-CoV yana aiki a matsayin kyakkyawan misali na yaduwar jinsuna daga jemage zuwa raƙuma na dromedary kuma daga raƙuma na dromedary zuwa mutane.
Asalin juyin halitta na MERS-CoV daga jemage an san shi a farkon gano shi kuma an kuma ƙarfafa shi ta binciken da aka samu daga baya.
A bayyane yake cewa jemage suna samar da wadataccen nau'in ƙwayoyin cuta don musayar ɓangarorin kwayoyin halitta da watsawa tsakanin jinsuna.
Tsawon rai, yankuna masu yawa, hulɗar zamantakewar jama'a da kuma ƙarfin tashi duk yanayi ne mai kyau ga bats don zama 'mai yaduwar kwayar cutar'.
A gefe guda kuma, an gabatar da MERS-CoV ga raƙuman dromedary shekaru da yawa.
Ya dace da waɗannan raƙuman da suka canza daga mai watsa shiri na tsakiya zuwa mai karɓar ruwa mai ɗorewa da na halitta.
MERS-CoV yana haifar da rashin lafiya mai sauƙi kuma yana riƙe da ƙarancin canjin canji a cikin waɗannan dabbobin.
Yaduwar sa zuwa ga mutane ba zato ba tsammani ne kuma mutane suna ci gaba da kasancewa mai karɓar baƙi na MERS-CoV saboda ba za a iya ci gaba da yaduwar sa ba.
Sabanin rawar raƙuma wajen watsa MERS-CoV, rawar pangolins, idan akwai, a cikin watsa SARS-CoV-2 ta bambanta.
Musamman, pangolin beta-CoVs suna da cutarwa sosai a cikin pangolins.
Suna iya zama mahalarta mara kyau ga beta-CoVs masu alaƙa da SARS-CoV-2, kwatankwacin civets a cikin yanayin SARS-CoV.
Akwai yiwuwar da dama na yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 daga dabbobi zuwa mutane a cikin ko kuma a cire su a cikin binciken nan gaba.
Na farko, jemage na iya zama mai riƙe da kwayar cutar da ke da alaƙa da SARS-CoV-2 kusan daidai da SARS-CoV-2.
Mutane na iya raba yanayin muhalli tare da jemage ta hanyar yanka ko hakar ma'adinai.
Na biyu, pangolins na iya zama ɗaya daga cikin matsakaitan masu haɓaka mai watsa shiri wanda sabon kwayar cutar da ke da alaƙa da SARS-CoV-2 aka gabatar da ita.
Mutane suna kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar yanka da cin naman farauta.
Yana yiwuwa dabbobi masu shayarwa da yawa ciki har da dabbobin gida suna da saukin kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2.
Ana buƙatar binciken dabbobi na gida da na daji don ƙwayoyin cuta.
Na uku, kamar yadda aka ambata a sama, sake haɗuwa da daidaitawa na SARS-CoV-2 na iya faruwa a cikin nau'in na uku wanda ke da alaƙa da duka bat da pangolins.
Har yanzu ana ci gaba da binciken asalin SARS-CoV-2 daga dabbobi.
Baya ga nau'ikan nau'ikan dabbobi daban-daban, manyan abubuwa uku a gefen kwayar cutar suna da mahimmanci wajen sauƙaƙe CoVs don ƙetare shingen jinsuna.
Da farko dai, yawan canjin halittarsu a cikin kwafin RNA.
Idan aka kwatanta da sauran ƙwayoyin cuta na RNA guda ɗaya, ƙididdigar canjin canjin CoVs ana iya ɗauka a matsayin  matsakaici  zuwa  mai girma  tare da matsakaicin canjin canji na ~ 10-4 sauyawa a kowace shekara a kowane shafin 2, dangane da matakin daidaitawar CoV zuwa sabbin masu karɓar baƙi.
CoVs suna da exoribonuclease mai karantawa, cirewa wanda ke haifar da canji mai yawa da raguwa ko ma rashin rayuwa.
Abin sha'awa, ana san analogue na nucleotide Remdesivir don hana kwayar cutar CoV ta hanyar hana wannan exoribonuclease da RNA-dogara RNA polymerase.
Remdesivir yana ɗaya daga cikin mafi kyawun magungunan anti-SARS-CoV-2 da za a gwada a cikin gwaji na asibiti.
Duk da haka, yawan canjin CoVs ya fi na masu karɓar su sau miliyan.
Bugu da kari, yawan canjin halitta yakan yi yawa idan CoVs ba su dace da mai gidan ba.
Idan aka kwatanta da SARS-CoV tare da babban canjin canji, canjin canjin SARS-CoV-2 a bayyane ya fi ƙasa, yana nuna matakin daidaitawa da mutane.
Wataƙila, ya riga ya daidaita da wani mai ba da abinci da ke kusa da mutane.
Baya ga SARS-CoV-2, wannan ma ya shafi MERS-CoV, wanda ya dace da raƙuman dromedary.
A ka'idar, ba zai yiwu ba cewa jujjuyawar kwayoyin halitta za ta sa alluran rigakafi da maganin rigakafin cutar SARS-CoV-2 ba su da tasiri da sauri.
Na biyu, babban RNA genome a cikin CoVs yana amfani da ƙarin filastik a cikin gyaran genome don maye gurbi da sake haɗawa, don haka yana ƙaruwa da yiwuwar co-juyin halitta tsakanin jinsuna, wanda ke da fa'ida ga fitowar sabbin CoVs lokacin da yanayi ya dace.
Wannan yana tallafawa ta hanyar ɗakunan karatu na musamman da kuma ayyukan furotin da aka tsara zuwa ƙarshen 3 'na kwayoyin halitta.
Na uku, CoVs bazuwar kuma sau da yawa suna canza samfuran yayin sakewa na RNA ta hanyar tsari na musamman  kwafin-zaɓi.
A cikin mai masaukin da ke aiki a matsayin jirgin ruwa mai haɗawa, sauya zaren yana faruwa sau da yawa yayin rubutun CoV RNA.
RNAs masu cikakken tsayi da kuma subgenomic masu kama da juna zasu iya sake haɗuwa don samar da sababbin CoVs.
An sami shaidar ilimin halitta na sake haɗuwa ta halitta a cikin duka HCoV-HKU1 da HCoV-OC43, da kuma CoVs na dabbobi kamar su bat SL-CoV da batCoV-HKU9.
Hadin gwiwar kwayar cutar da mai masaukin baki dangane da watsawa
Baya ga abubuwan da ke tattare da kwayar cutar guda uku da aka ambata a sama, hulɗar kwayar cutar tare da mai karɓar mai karɓar wani mahimmin abu ne mai tasiri kan watsawa tsakanin jinsuna.
A nan, ana ɗaukar sake haɗuwa da SARS-CoV a matsayin misali na yau da kullun, wanda kuma ya nuna shaidar zabin tabbatacce yayin abubuwan watsawa tsakanin jinsuna.
Dangane da nazarin kwatancen tsakanin keɓaɓɓu na SARS-CoVs na mutum da civet, ana tsammanin SARS-CoV yana fuskantar saurin daidaitawa a cikin masu watsawa daban-daban, musamman tare da maye gurbi a RBD na furotin S.
Gabaɗaya, RBD a cikin furotin S na CoV yana hulɗa tare da mai karɓar ƙwayoyin cuta kuma ana zaɓar shi sosai ta hanyar amsawar ƙwayoyin cuta.
A cikin SARS-CoV, RBD yana cikin amino acid na 318 zuwa 510 akan ɓangaren S1, wanda ke ɗaure da ACE2 na ɗan adam da kuma masu karɓar sa don shigar da kwayar cutar.
RBD na SARS-CoV na iya gane masu karɓar ACE2 na dabbobi daban-daban, gami da bat, civet, linzamin kwamfuta da kare raccoon, yana ba da damar watsa kwayar cutar tsakanin jinsuna.
A zahiri, an lura da ragowar amino acid 6 ne kawai daban da na mutum da na civet virus a cikin RBD kuma 4 daga cikinsu suna cikin abin da ke ɗaure mai karɓar don hulɗa tare da mai karɓar ACE2.
Civet SARS-CoV yana da canjin K479N da S487T a cikin RBD, wanda zai iya haɓaka alaƙar hulɗar furotin mai ƙwanƙwasa tare da mai karɓar ACE2 na ɗan adam.
A wasu kalmomin, waɗannan maye gurbin amino acid guda biyu na iya zama mahimmanci ga daidaitawar kwayar cutar ga mutane.
Yana da mahimmanci cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana da masu karɓar ƙwayoyin cuta iri ɗaya da SARS-CoV.
Bambanci 30% tsakanin SARS-CoV-2 da SARS-CoV a cikin S1 na S protein yana nuna cewa alaƙar haɗin S protein tare da ACE2 na ɗan adam na iya canzawa.
A zahiri, binciken cryo-EM ya nuna kusancin wannan haɗin ya ninka sau 10 zuwa 20 fiye da na tsakanin ACE2 na ɗan adam da furotin SARS-CoV S.
Hakanan zai zama mai ban sha'awa don ƙayyade ko ana buƙatar wani mai karɓar coreceptor don watsa SARS-CoV-2.
Abin sha'awa, HCoV-NL63 kuma yana ɗaure da ACE2 amma tare da wani ɓangare na S.
Akwai sauran masu karɓar HCoV da yawa, kamar aminopeptidase N don HCoV-229E, da 9-O-acetylated sialic acid don HCoV-OC43.
Hakanan zasu iya bayyana nasarar daidaita waɗannan CoVs a cikin mutane bayan watsawa tsakanin jinsuna daga masu karɓar dabbobi.
Baya ga masu karɓar ƙwayoyin cuta, sakamakon watsawar HCoVs tsakanin jinsuna yana kuma ƙarƙashin sauran abubuwan dogaro da ƙuntatawa.
Bambancin waɗannan sunadarai masu karɓar baƙi tsakanin mutane da masu karɓar baƙi na HCoVs na halitta kamar bats, dromedary raƙuma da rodents na iya zama shinge ga watsa tsakanin jinsuna.
HCoVs dole ne su mamaye abubuwan dogaro da mai masauki kuma su kawar da abubuwan ƙuntatawa na mai masauki don samun nasarar watsawa tsakanin jinsuna.
A wannan batun, ƙayyadaddun kwayoyin halitta a cikin wannan muhimmin yanki na hulɗar ƙwayoyin cuta-mai watsa shiri har yanzu ana ganowa da halayyar su.
Binciken da ba shi da son kai na dukkanin kwayoyin halitta na dogara da mai masauki da kuma ƙuntatawa ga SARS-CoV-2 ta amfani da fasahar zamani ta CRISPR na iya zama mai amfani.
Fitowar sabbin HCoVs: komawa zuwa wuri na farko
Bambancin CoVs na bera yana ba da dama mai yawa don fitowar sabbin HCoVs.
A wannan ma'anar, CoVs na bera suna aiki azaman tarin kwayoyin halittar HCoVs.
Bugu da ƙari, sauye-sauye mai sauri da sake haɗuwa da kwayoyin halitta suma suna haifar da juyin halittar HCoV kuma suna aiki a matsayin matakai biyu masu mahimmanci a cikin wannan aikin.
Misali, saye ko asarar sabbin kwayoyin halittar furotin suna da damar canza yanayin kwayar cutar sosai.
Daga cikin furotin na SARS-CoV, an yi tunanin ORF8 yana da mahimmanci wajen daidaitawa da mutane, kamar yadda aka ware ƙwayoyin cuta na SARS-CoV amma an gano cewa suna ɓoye furotin ORF8 daban.
An gano wani nau'in cirewar nucleotide 29 na SARS-CoVs a cikin nau'ikan da aka ware a farkon annobar ɗan adam.
Wannan cirewa ya raba ORF8 zuwa ORF8a da ORF8b kuma ana tunanin cewa canji ne na daidaitawa wanda ke inganta sauyawar masu masaukin baki.
Bugu da ƙari, SARS-CoV yana da tarihin sake haɗuwa tare da zuriyar alpha- da gamma-CoVs, inda aka gano ƙananan ƙananan yankuna a cikin RNA-dogara RNA polymerase.
An kuma gano wuraren sake haɗuwa a cikin nsp9, yawancin nsp10, da kuma sassan nsp14.
Hakanan, an nuna cewa annobar MERS-CoV ta sami abubuwan haɗuwa tsakanin zuriyoyi daban-daban, wanda ya faru a cikin raƙuman dromedary a Saudi Arabiya.
Baya ga SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, an kuma lura da abubuwan sake haɗuwa a cikin sauran HCoVs, wanda HCoVs ke sake haɗuwa tare da sauran CoVs na dabbobi a cikin ƙwayoyin halittar su.
Hakanan yakamata a yi gargadi cewa zabin wucin gadi na iya ba da gudummawa ga canje-canje da ba a so a cikin kwayoyin halittar kwayar cuta, mai yiwuwa sakamakon sauƙaƙe ƙwayoyin cuta daga matsin zaɓin da aka yi, kamar ta tsarin rigakafin mai masaukin.
Misali na waɗannan tasirin shine asarar cikakken ORF4 a cikin samfurin samfurin HCoV-229E, saboda cirewar nucleotide biyu.
Duk da yake ana iya lura da cikakkiyar ORF4 a cikin ƙwayoyin cuta na bat da raƙumi da ke da alaƙa da HCoV-229E, alpha-CoV na alpaca yana nuna shigar da nucleotide guda ɗaya, wanda ke haifar da canjin firam.
A ƙarshe amma ba mafi ƙaranci ba, juyin halitta na sabon HCoVs kuma ana motsa shi ta hanyar matsin zaɓin a cikin masu riƙe da su.
An gano alamun rashin bayyanar cututtuka ko kuma kawai alamu masu sauƙi lokacin da kwari suka kamu da CoVs, wanda ke nuna daidaitawar juna tsakanin CoVs da kwari.
Ya bayyana cewa jemage sun dace da CoVs a zahiri da kuma ilimin lissafi.
Misali, lahani a cikin kunnawar amsawar kumburi a cikin jemage yana rage cututtukan da CoVs ke haifar da su yadda ya kamata.
Bugu da ƙari, aikin ƙwayoyin halitta na halitta a cikin bats an hana shi saboda haɓakar mai karɓar ƙwayar halitta mai kisan kai NKG2/CD94 da ƙananan matakin bayyana manyan kwayoyin halittar ƙwayar cuta na I.
Bugu da ƙari, babban matakin nau'ikan oxygen masu aiki (ROS) da aka samar daga babban aikin metabolism na jemage na iya hana CoV sakewa kuma yana shafar gyara ta hanyar exoribonuclease, don haka samar da matsin lamba don samar da ƙwayoyin cuta masu cutarwa sosai lokacin da aka gabatar da su cikin sabon mai masauki.
Ƙarin ƙwayar CoV mai cutarwa na iya haɓaka ta hanyar sake haɗuwa, wanda ke haifar da samun sabbin sunadarai ko fasalolin sunadarai don daidaitawar mai masauki.
Don haka, ba daidaituwa ba ne cewa sabbin HCoVs uku sun fito a cikin shekaru ashirin da suka gabata.
CoVs ba su da cutar ko haifar da alamun rashin lafiya a cikin masu riƙe da su kamar bats da raƙuma.
Suna yin kwafi sosai ba tare da haifar da amsa mai karfi ba.
A nan ne asirin dalilin da yasa ake ganin masu dauke da cutar ba tare da alamomi ba da kuma abin da ke haifar da mummunan yanayin kamuwa da cutar a cikin mutane.
Manyan alamun galibi saboda yawan aiki ne na amsawar rigakafi da kuma guguwar cytokine inda mafi ƙarfin amsawar rigakafi, mafi tsananin lalacewar huhu.
Sabanin haka, a cikin masu ɗaukar alamun, an cire amsar rigakafi daga maimaita CoV.
Hanyar da ta dace ta cire haɗin maganin rigakafi na iya samun sakamako mai amfani a cikin maganin anti-SARS-CoV-2.
Amsar interferon tana da ƙarfi musamman a cikin bat.
Don haka, gudanar da nau'in I interferon aƙalla a farkon matakin kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a cikin mutane ya kamata ya zama da amfani.
Bugu da kari, NLRP3 kunnawa mai kumburi a cikin bat yana da lahani.
Ta wannan dalili, hana NLRP3 inflammasome tare da MCC950 na iya zama da amfani a maganin COVID-19.
Fitowar SARS-CoV-2 ya biyo bayan babban jigon da SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV suka taso.
Yayin da aka gano beta-CoV na bera wanda ke da kashi 95% na nucleotide homology tare da SARS-CoV, akwai kuma bat-CoV wanda ke da kashi 96% na nucleotide homology tare da SARS-CoV-2.
Yayin da aka gano civets da sauran dabbobi a kasuwanni suna dauke da ƙwayoyin cuta iri ɗaya da SARS-CoV, ba a gano masu karɓar bakuncin SARS-CoV-2 ba.
An gano pangolin beta-CoVs masu kama da SARS-CoV-2, wanda ke nuna cewa pangolins na iya zama ɗaya daga cikin masu karɓar baƙi na tsakiya ko pangolin beta-CoVs na iya ba da gudummawar gutsuttsarin kwayoyin halitta zuwa sigar ƙarshe ta SARS-CoV-2.
Kodayake tambayoyi sun kasance, babu wata hujja da ke nuna cewa SARS-CoV-2 mutum ne ya yi shi da gangan ko kuma ba da gangan ba.
CoVs sun dawo cikin hasken haske saboda barkewar cutar SARS-CoV-2 kwanan nan.
Nazarin CoVs a cikin jemage da sauran dabbobi ya canza ra'ayinmu game da mahimmancin asalin dabbobi da wuraren ajiyar dabbobi na HCoVs a cikin watsawa ga mutane.
Shaida mai yawa ta nuna cewa SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2 suna da asalin bera kuma ana watsa su ga mutane ta hanyar masu watsawa na tsakiya.
Ganin cewa kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV ta samo asali ne daga hulɗa tsakanin mutane da civets a kasuwanni, rufe kasuwanni masu ɗumi da kashe civets a can na iya kawo ƙarshen annobar SARS.
Ta wannan dalili, ya kamata a cire pangolins daga kasuwannin rigar don hana yaduwar cutar zoonotic, saboda gano yawancin zuriyar pangolin beta-CoVs da ke da alaƙa da SARS-CoV-2.
Koyaya, ko kuma yadda SARS-CoV-2 ke yaduwa ga mutane ta hanyar pangolins da sauran dabbobi masu shayarwa har yanzu ba a bayyana su ba a cikin binciken da za a yi a nan gaba.
A gefe guda, MERS-CoV ya wanzu a cikin raƙuman dromedary na dogon lokaci.
Wadannan raƙuma suna aiki a matsayin muhimmin kayan aiki don sufuri da kuma babban tushen nama, madara, fata da kayayyakin ulu ga mazauna yankin.
An rarraba su ko'ina cikin Gabas ta Tsakiya da Afirka.
Saboda haka ba zai yiwu a sadaukar da dukkan raƙuma don sarrafa MERS ba, kamar yadda aka yi a kasuwannin dabbobi a China don hana yaduwar SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2.
Don dakatar da sake barkewar cutar MERS, ya kamata a ɗauki cikakkiyar hanyar haɓaka alluran rigakafi masu tasiri akan MERS-CoV don raƙuma, a hade tare da sauran matakan sarrafa kamuwa da cuta.
Tunda ba za mu iya kawar da waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta ba, sabbin nau'ikan ƙwayoyin cuta na iya fitowa don haifar da barkewar cutar.
Yawancin CoVs masu cutar dabbobi suna yawo a cikin daji.
Musamman, CoVs na bera tare da yuwuwar cutar dabbobi sun bambanta sosai.
Akwai dama da yawa cewa waɗannan CoVs na zoonotic sun samo asali kuma sun sake haɗuwa, wanda ke haifar da fitowar sabbin CoVs waɗanda ke da saurin yaduwa da / ko kisa a cikin mutane a nan gaba.
Dole ne a daina al'adar cin namun daji a wasu wurare na kasar Sin domin rage hulɗar da ba dole ba tsakanin mutane da dabbobi.
Tare da wahalar SARS, MERS da COVID-19, yakamata a sami shiri da shirin amsawa mafi kyau.
A gaskiya, akwai ƙwayoyin cuta da yawa a duniya na dogon lokaci.
Suna zama a cikin tafkunan su na halitta har sai akwai damar yaduwa.
Ko da yake jemage suna da halaye da yawa da ke sa yaduwar ƙwayoyin cuta, ana iya rage damar da mutane za su iya haɗuwa da jemage da sauran dabbobin daji idan an koya wa mutane su guji su.
Ana buƙatar ci gaba da sa ido a cikin dabbobi masu shayarwa don fahimtar yanayin CoVs da masu karɓar su na halitta, wanda zai zama da amfani wajen hana watsawa daga dabba zuwa mutum da ɓarkewar gaba.
A ƙarshe, hanya mafi inganci don hana cutar dabbobi ta hanyar kwayar cutar ita ce mutane su nisanta kansu daga wuraren da ke da alamun halitta na ƙwayoyin cutar.
Har yanzu akwai wasu abubuwa da suka ɓace a cikin wuyar warwarewa game da asalin SARS-CoV-2.
Da farko, idan kwari sun watsa kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 ga pangolins, zai zama da ban sha'awa ganin a wane yanayi kwari da pangolins zasu iya raba wuri ɗaya na muhalli.
Na biyu, idan kwari suna taka rawa kai tsaye wajen yaduwar cutar ga mutane, ya kamata a tantance yadda mutane ke hulɗa da kwari.
Na uku, idan dabba mai shayarwa ta uku tana aiki a matsayin mai watsa shiri na gaskiya, yadda yake hulɗa da nau'ikan daban-daban ciki har da mutane, bats da pangolins dole ne a bayyana.
A ƙarshe, tunda dabbobi masu shayarwa da yawa ciki har da dabbobin gida na iya zama masu saukin kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2, yakamata a gudanar da sa ido da kamuwa da cuta na gwaji.
Idan kwaro ne, pangolin ko wani dabba mai shayarwa, ana tsammanin cewa SARS-CoV-2 ko ƙwayoyin cuta na iyayensa waɗanda kusan iri ɗaya ne za a gano su a cikin masu ba da ita na halitta a nan gaba.
Ci gaba da bincike a wannan yanki zai bayyana hanyar juyin halitta na SARS-CoV-2 a cikin dabbobi, tare da mahimman tasiri a cikin rigakafi da sarrafa COVID-19 a cikin mutane.
Ana buƙatar sabunta ƙa'idodin bincike na COVID-19 wanda ake zargi da cutar da wanda aka tabbatar da cutar
A ranar 6 ga Fabrairun 2020, ƙungiyarmu ta buga jagorar shawara mai sauri don ganewa da maganin cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (2019-nCoV), kuma wannan jagorar ta ba da kwarewarmu kuma ta zama kyakkyawan tunani don yaƙi da wannan annobar a duk duniya.
Koyaya, cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) sabuwar cuta ce, hankalinmu da iliminmu suna ƙaruwa a hankali bisa ga binciken bincike da ke gudana da kuma kwarewar aikin asibiti; saboda haka, dabarun bincike da magani suma ana sabunta su koyaushe.
A cikin wannan wasikar, mun amsa tsokaci guda kan jagorarmu kuma mun samar da sabbin ka'idojin bincike na wanda ake zargi da cutar da wanda aka tabbatar da cutar bisa ga sabuwar Jagorar Ganowa da Kula da COVID-19 (siffa ta bakwai) da Kwamitin Kiwon Lafiyar Jama'ar Sin ya bayar.
A watan Disamba na 2019, sabon coronavirus na 2019 (2019-nCoV) ya haifar da barkewar cutar, wanda yanzu aka sanya masa suna a hukumance a matsayin cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) kuma an sanya wa kwayar cutar suna mai tsanani mai tsanani coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, WHO ta bayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
Don yaƙi da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2, ƙungiyarmu ta haɓaka jagorar shawara mai sauri kuma an buga ta kan layi a cikin Binciken Likita na Soja a ranar 06 ga Fabrairu 2020.
An yi amfani da shi sosai tun lokacin da aka buga shi.
Ka lura duk da haka cewa COVID-19 sabuwar cuta ce, wayar da kanmu da iliminmu suna ƙaruwa a hankali bisa ga binciken bincike da ke gudana da kuma kwarewar aikin asibiti; saboda haka, dabarun bincike da magani suma ana sabunta su koyaushe.
Misali, Jagororin Bincike da Kula da COVID-19 da Kwamitin Kiwon Lafiya na Jama'ar Sin (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/) ya bayar, tsakanin 16 ga Janairu 2020 zuwa 3 ga Maris 2020, ya fitar da jimlar bugu bakwai tare da wasu mahallin da aka canza sosai.
