Hukumomin kiwon lafiya a Wuhan, China (babban birnin lardin Hubei) sun ba da rahoton tarin cututtukan ciwon huhu da ba a san dalilin su ba a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, kuma an fara bincike a farkon Janairu 2020.
