Kwayar cutar da ta haifar da barkewar cutar an san ta da SARS-CoV-2, sabuwar kwayar cutar da aka gano da ke da alaƙa da kwayar cutar coronaviruses, pangolin coronaviruses, da SARS-CoV. An gano daga baya cewa farkon mutumin da aka sani da alamun cutar ya kamu da rashin lafiya a ranar 1 ga Disamba, 2019, kuma wannan mutumin ba shi da alaƙa da alamar kasuwa mai zafi.
Daga cikin rukunin farko na shari'o'in da aka ruwaito a watan Disamba na 2019, kashi biyu bisa uku an gano cewa suna da alaƙa da kasuwa.
A ranar 13 ga Maris, 2020, wani rahoto da ba a tabbatar da shi ba daga South China Morning Post ya nuna cewa wani lamari da aka gano a ranar 17 ga Nuwamba, 2019, a cikin wani mutum mai shekaru 55 daga lardin Hubei, na iya zama na farko. A ranar 26 ga Fabrairu, 2020, WHO ta ba da rahoton cewa, yayin da sabbin shari'o'in da aka ruwaito sun ragu a China amma ba zato ba tsammani suka karu a Italiya, Iran, da Koriya ta Kudu, yawan sabbin shari'o'in da ke wajen China ya zarce adadin sabbin shari'o'in da ke cikin China a karon farko.
Akwai yiwuwar rashin yawan rahotanni, musamman a tsakanin wadanda ke da alamun rashin lafiya.
Zuwa 26 ga watan Fabrairu, an samu karancin masu kamuwa da cutar a tsakanin matasa, wadanda shekarunsu 19 zuwa kasa da haka sun kai kashi 2.4% na masu kamuwa da cutar a duniya. Babban mai ba da shawara kan kimiyya na Burtaniya, Patrick Vallance, ya kiyasta cewa kashi 60% na yawan mutanen Burtaniya za su buƙaci kamuwa da cutar kafin a sami ingantacciyar rigakafin garken.
Yanayi yana nufin yawan mutanen da aka gwada don COVID-19, kuma wanda aka tabbatar da gwajin ya tabbata bisa ga ƙa'idodin hukuma.
Har zuwa 23 ga Maris, babu wata ƙasa da ta gwada fiye da kashi 3% na yawanta, kuma ƙasashe da yawa suna da manufofin hukuma na ba da gwaji ga waɗanda ke da alamun rashin lafiya kawai, kamar Italiya, Netherlands, Spain, da Switzerland.
Wani bincike da aka buga a ranar 16 ga watan Maris ya gano cewa a China, har zuwa 23 ga watan Janairu, kimanin kashi 86% na kamuwa da COVID-19 ba a gano su ba, kuma waɗannan kamuwa da cutar da ba a rubuta ba sune tushen kamuwa da cutar ga kashi 79% na shari'o'in da aka rubuta.
Wani bincike na kididdiga da aka buga a ranar 30 ga Maris ya kiyasta cewa yawan masu kamuwa da cutar a Italiya ya fi yawan wadanda aka ruwaito.
Ƙididdigar farko na ƙididdigar ƙididdigar asali (R0) don COVID-19 ya kasance 1.4 zuwa 2.4.
Wani bincike da Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cututtuka ta Amurka ta wallafa ya kammala cewa zai iya zama 5.7.
