Waɗannan lambobin sun bambanta ta yanki da lokaci, kuma suna shafar yawan gwajin, ingancin tsarin kiwon lafiya, zaɓuɓɓukan magani, lokaci tun farkon barkewar cutar, da halayen jama'a kamar shekaru, jinsi, da lafiyar gaba ɗaya.
Dangane da ƙididdigar Jami'ar Johns Hopkins, adadin mutuwar duniya zuwa shari'ar shine 6.0% (97,039/1,617,204) kamar na 10 ga Afrilu 2020.
