Wadannan ƙididdigar ba su da iyakacin lokaci kuma suna bin takamaiman yawan jama'a daga kamuwa da cuta zuwa warwarewar shari'ar.
Masana da yawa sun yi ƙoƙarin lissafin waɗannan lambobin don takamaiman mutane.
Cibiyar Nazarin Magunguna ta Jami'ar Oxford ta kiyasta cewa yawan kamuwa da cutar a cikin annobar gaba ɗaya yana tsakanin 0.1% da 0.39%.
Ƙididdigar sama na wannan zangon ya dace da sakamakon gwajin bazuwar farko don COVID-19 a Jamus, da kuma nazarin ƙididdigar nazarin tasirin gwaji akan ƙididdigar CFR.
WHO ta tabbatar da cewa za a iya sarrafa annobar.
