A ranar 23 ga watan Maris, Iran tana fuskantar sabbin mutane 50 a kowace awa da kuma sabon mutuwa a kowane minti goma saboda coronavirus.
A cewar wani jami'in WHO, akwai yiwuwar akwai karin mutane biyar da suka kamu da cutar a Iran fiye da yadda ake bayar da rahoton.
An kuma nuna cewa takunkumin da Amurka ta kakaba wa Iran na iya shafar karfin tattalin arzikin kasar wajen magance cutar.
Babban Kwamishinan Majalisar Dinkin Duniya na Kare Hakkin Dan Adam ya bukaci a sassauta takunkumin tattalin arziki ga kasashen da cutar ta fi shafa, ciki har da Iran.
An tabbatar da barkewar cutar zuwa Italiya a ranar 31 ga Janairu, lokacin da wasu 'yan yawon bude ido' yan China biyu suka gwada tabbatacce ga SARS-CoV-2 a Rome.
Yanayin ya fara ƙaruwa sosai, wanda ya sa gwamnatin Italiya ta dakatar da duk jiragen da ke zuwa da dawowa daga China kuma ta ayyana dokar ta baci.
Daga baya an gano tarin marasa alaƙa na COVID-19 lokuta, farawa da tabbatar da shari'o'i 16 a Lombardy a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu. A ranar 22 ga Fabrairu, Majalisar Ministoci ta ba da sanarwar sabon doka don hana barkewar cutar, gami da keɓe mutane sama da 50,000 daga garuruwa daban-daban 11 a arewacin Italiya.
Firayim Minista Giuseppe Conte ya ce, "A yankunan da cutar ta bulla, ba za a ba da izinin shiga da fita ba. "
An riga an ba da umarnin dakatar da ayyukan aiki da abubuwan wasanni a waɗannan yankuna. "A ranar 4 ga Maris, gwamnatin Italiya ta ba da umarnin rufe dukkan makarantu da jami'o'i a duk faɗin ƙasar yayin da Italiya ta kai mutuwar 100".
Duk manyan abubuwan wasanni, gami da wasannin kwallon kafa na Serie A, za a gudanar da su a rufe har zuwa Afrilu, amma a ranar 9 ga Maris, an dakatar da duk wasanni gaba ɗaya na aƙalla wata ɗaya.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, Firayim Minista Conte ya ba da umarnin dakatar da kusan duk ayyukan kasuwanci ban da manyan kantuna da kantunan magani. A ranar 6 ga Maris, Kwalejin Italiya na Anesthesia, Analgesia, Resuscitation da Kulawa mai tsanani (SIAARTI) ta buga shawarwarin ɗabi'ar likita game da hanyoyin rarrabuwa da za a iya amfani da su.
A ranar 19 ga watan Maris, Italiya ta wuce China a matsayin ƙasa da ta fi yawan mutuwar da ke da nasaba da cutar coronavirus a duniya bayan ta ba da rahoton mutuwar 3,405 daga cutar.
A ranar 22 ga Maris, an ba da rahoton cewa Rasha ta aika da jiragen sama na soja tara tare da kayan aikin likita zuwa Italiya.
Ya zuwa ranar 5 ga Afrilu, akwai mutane 128,948 da aka tabbatar da cutar, 15,887 da suka mutu, da kuma 21,815 da suka warke a Italiya, tare da yawancin waɗannan cututtukan da ke faruwa a yankin Lombardy.
Wani rahoto na CNN ya nuna cewa haɗuwa da yawan tsofaffin mutanen Italiya da rashin iya gwada duk waɗanda ke da kwayar cutar har zuwa yau na iya ba da gudummawa ga yawan mutuwar.
Amsar da Burtaniya ta bayar ga kwayar cutar ta fara fitowa a matsayin daya daga cikin ƙasashe masu nutsuwa, kuma har zuwa 18 ga Maris 2020, gwamnatin Burtaniya ba ta sanya kowane nau'in nisantar zamantakewa ko matakan killace jama'a ga 'yan ƙasa ba.
A sakamakon haka, gwamnati ta sami suka saboda rashin saurin da ake ganin ba shi da ƙarfi a cikin martani ga damuwar da jama'a ke fuskanta. A ranar 16 ga Maris, Firayim Minista Boris Johnson ya ba da sanarwar da ke ba da shawara game da duk balaguron da ba dole ba da kuma hulɗar zamantakewa, yana ba da shawarar mutane su yi aiki daga gida idan ya yiwu kuma su guji wurare kamar mashaya, gidajen abinci, da gidajen wasan kwaikwayo.
A ranar 20 ga Maris, gwamnati ta sanar da cewa duk wuraren shakatawa kamar mashaya da wuraren motsa jiki za su rufe da wuri-wuri, kuma ta yi alkawarin biyan kashi 80% na albashin ma'aikata har zuwa iyakar £ 2,500 a kowane wata don hana rashin aikin yi a cikin rikicin. A ranar 23 ga Maris, Firayim Minista ya sanar da tsauraran matakan nisantar zamantakewa, hana tarurruka na mutane sama da biyu da kuma iyakance tafiya da ayyukan waje zuwa abin da aka ɗauka ya zama dole.
Ba kamar matakan da suka gabata ba, 'yan sanda sun tilasta wa wadannan takunkumi ta hanyar ba da tarurruka da kuma tarwatsa tarurruka.
" An umarci yawancin kasuwancin su rufe, ban da kasuwancin da aka ɗauka ""muhimmanci"", gami da manyan kantuna, kantin magani, bankuna, shagunan kayan aiki, tashoshin mai, da gareji. "
A ranar 20 ga Janairu, an tabbatar da sanannen shari'ar farko ta COVID-19 a jihar Washington da ke Arewa maso Yammacin Pacific a cikin wani mutum da ya dawo daga Wuhan a ranar 15 ga Janairu.
An kafa Rukunin Ayyukan Coronavirus na Fadar White House a ranar 29 ga Janairu.
A ranar 31 ga Janairu, gwamnatin Trump ta ayyana dokar ta baci ta kiwon lafiya, kuma ta sanya takunkumi kan shiga ga matafiya daga China.
A ranar 28 ga Janairun 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtukababbar cibiyar kiwon lafiyar jama'a ta gwamnatin Amurkata sanar da cewa sun haɓaka kayan gwajin kansu.
Duk da haka, Amurka ta yi jinkirin farawa a cikin gwaji, wanda ya ɓoye ainihin yaduwar cutar a lokacin.
Gwajin ya lalace saboda kayan gwajin da gwamnatin tarayya ta samar a watan Fabrairu, rashin amincewar gwamnatin tarayya ga kayan gwajin da ba na gwamnati ba (ta masana kimiyya, kamfanoni da asibitoci) har zuwa ƙarshen Fabrairu, da kuma ƙuntatawa ga mutane don cancanta don gwaji har zuwa farkon Maris (ana buƙatar umarnin likita bayan haka).
Zuwa 27 ga watan Fabrairu, The Washington Post ta ruwaito an gudanar da gwaje-gwaje kasa da 4,000 a Amurka.
Zuwa 13 ga watan Maris, The Atlantic ta ruwaito cewa an gudanar da gwaje-gwaje kasa da 14,000.
A ranar 22 ga Maris, Associated Press ta ruwaito: "Mutane da yawa da ke da alamomi da umarnin likita sun jira awanni ko kwanaki don gwaji. "Bayan an ba da rahoton mutuwar farko a Amurka a jihar Washington a ranar 29 ga Fabrairu, Gwamna Jay Inslee ya ayyana dokar ta baci, matakin da wasu jihohi suka bi ba da daɗewa ba. "
Makarantu a yankin Seattle sun soke azuzuwan a ranar 3 ga Maris, kuma a tsakiyar watan Maris, makarantu a duk faɗin ƙasar sun rufe. A ranar 6 ga Maris, 2020, an shawarci Amurka game da hasashen tasirin sabon coronavirus a ƙasar ta ƙungiyar masana cututtukan cututtuka a Kwalejin Imperial ta London.
A wannan ranar Shugaba Trump ya rattaba hannu kan Dokar Shirye-shiryen Coronavirus da Amsawa da Ƙarin Kuɗaɗen Kuɗi, wanda ya samar da dala biliyan 8.3 a cikin kuɗin gaggawa don hukumomin tarayya don amsa cutar.
Kamfanoni sun sanya takunkumin tafiye-tafiye ga ma'aikata, sun soke taro, kuma sun ƙarfafa ma'aikata su yi aiki daga gida.
An soke abubuwan wasanni da yanayi. A ranar 11 ga Maris, Trump ya sanar da takunkumin hana tafiye-tafiye ga yawancin Turai, ban da Burtaniya, na kwanaki 30, wanda ya fara aiki a ranar 13 ga Maris.
Kashegari, ya faɗaɗa ƙuntatawa don haɗa da Burtaniya da Ireland.
A ranar 13 ga Maris, ya ayyana dokar ta baci ta kasa, wanda ya samar da kudaden tarayya don amsa rikicin.
Farawa daga 15 ga Maris, yawancin kasuwancin sun rufe ko rage sa'o'i a duk faɗin Amurka don ƙoƙarin rage yaduwar kwayar cutar.
A ranar 17 ga watan Maris, an tabbatar da annobar a jihohi 50 da kuma gundumar Columbia. A ranar 23 ga watan Maris, an bayar da rahoton cewa New York City tana da mutane 10,700 da suka kamu da cutar coronavirus, fiye da jimlar adadin masu cutar a Koriya ta Kudu.
A ranar 25 ga Maris, gwamnan ya ce nisantar zamantakewar jama'a kamar tana aiki, yayin da ƙididdigar ninki biyu na lokuta ta ragu daga kwanaki 2.0 zuwa kwanaki 4.7.
Ya zuwa ranar 28 ga watan Maris, an samu mutane 32,308 da suka kamu da cutar a birnin New York, kuma mutane 672 sun mutu sakamakon cutar. A ranar 26 ga watan Maris, an bayar da rahoton cewa Amurka tana da mutane da yawa da suka kamu da cutar coronavirus fiye da kowace ƙasa a duniya, ciki har da China da Italiya. Ya zuwa ranar 8 ga Afrilu, an samu mutane 400,335 da suka kamu da cutar a Amurka, kuma mutane 12,841 sun mutu.
A cewar rahotannin kafofin watsa labarai a ranar 30 ga Maris, Shugaban Amurka Trump ya yanke shawarar tsawaita ƙa'idodin nisantar zamantakewa har zuwa 30 ga Afrilu.
A wannan ranar, jirgin ruwan asibiti mai ɗauke da gadaje 1,000 mai suna USNS Comfort ya kafa kafa a birnin New York.
A ranar 3 ga Afrilu, Amurka ta sami adadin mutuwar 884 saboda cutar coronavirus a cikin awanni 24.
A jihar New York, masu kamuwa da cutar sun zarce mutane 100,000 a ranar 3 ga Afrilu. An soki Fadar White House saboda rage girman barazanar da kuma sarrafa saƙon ta hanyar umarci jami'an kiwon lafiya da masana kimiyya da su daidaita maganganun jama'a da wallafe-wallafen da suka shafi cutar tare da ofishin Mataimakin Shugaban Mike Pence.
Gabaɗaya amincewa da yadda Trump ke kula da rikicin ya kasance mai rarrabuwa a cikin ƙungiyoyi.
Wasu jami'an Amurka da masu sharhi sun soki dogaro da Amurka kan shigo da kayan aiki masu mahimmanci, gami da kayan aikin likita masu mahimmanci, daga China.
An yi amfani da nazarin tsarin tafiye-tafiyen jirgin sama don tsarawa da tsinkayar yanayin yaduwa kuma an buga shi a cikin Jaridar Magungunan Balaguro a tsakiyar Janairu 2020.
Dangane da bayanan 2018 daga Transportungiyar Sufurin Jiragen Sama ta Duniya, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo, da Taipei suna da mafi yawan matafiya daga Wuhan.
An kuma bayar da rahoton cewa Dubai, Sydney, da Melbourne sanannun wurare ne ga mutanen da ke tafiya daga Wuhan.
Bali an ba da rahoton cewa ita ce mafi ƙarancin iyawa a cikin biranen 20 da aka fi so a cikin shirye-shirye, yayin da biranen Ostiraliya aka ɗauka mafi iyawa. Ostiraliya ta fitar da Tsarin Amsar Gaggawa don Sabon Coronavirus (COVID-19) a ranar 7 ga Fabrairu.
Ya bayyana cewa har yanzu ba a gano abubuwa da yawa game da COVID-19 ba, kuma cewa Ostiraliya za ta jaddada kula da kan iyakoki da sadarwa a cikin martani ga cutar.
A ranar 21 ga Maris, an ayyana gaggawa na lafiyar ɗan adam a Ostiraliya.
Saboda keɓewar sufuri na jama'a a Wuhan da Hubei, ƙasashe da yawa sun shirya kwashe 'yan ƙasa da ma'aikatan diflomasiyya daga yankin, musamman ta hanyar jiragen haya na ƙasar, tare da hukumomin China suna ba da izini.
Kasashen Kanada, Amurka, Japan, Indiya, Sri Lanka, Ostareliya, Faransa, Argentina, Jamus, da Thailand suna cikin na farko da suka shirya fitar da 'yan kasarsu.
Pakistan ta ce ba za ta kwashe wani dan kasar ta daga China ba.
A ranar 7 ga Fabrairu, Brazil ta kwashe 'yan Brazil 34 ko danginsu ban da 'yan Poland hudu, wani dan kasar Sin, da kuma dan kasar Indiya.
'Yan ƙasar Poland, China, da Indiya sun sauka a Poland, inda jirgin na Brazil ya tsaya kafin ya ci gaba da hanyarsa zuwa Brazil.
An killace 'yan kasar Brazil da suka je Wuhan a wani sansanin soji kusa da Brasília.
A wannan ranar, an kwashe 'yan Kanada 215 (176 daga jirgin farko, da 39 daga jirgin sama na biyu da gwamnatin Amurka ta yi haya) daga Wuhan zuwa CFB Trenton don keɓewa na makonni biyu.
A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, wani jirgin sama na 'yan Kanada 185 daga Wuhan ya sauka a CFB Trenton.
Hukumomin Ostiraliya sun kwashe 'yan ƙasa 277 a ranakun 3 da 4 ga watan Fabrairu zuwa Cibiyar Kula da Tsibirin Kirsimeti, wanda aka sake amfani da shi a matsayin cibiyar killacewa, inda suka kasance na kwanaki 14.
Jirgin saukar da mutanen New Zealand ya isa Auckland a ranar 5 ga Fabrairu; fasinjojinsa (gami da wasu daga Ostiraliya da Pacific) an killace su a sansanin sojan ruwa a Whangaparoa, arewacin Auckland.
A ranar 15 ga Fabrairu, Amurka ta sanar da cewa za ta kwashe Amurkawa a cikin jirgin ruwan Diamond Princess.
A ranar 21 ga Fabrairu, jirgin sama dauke da fasinjojin Kanada 129 da aka kwashe daga Diamond Princess ya sauka a Trenton, Ontario.
A farkon watan Maris, gwamnatin Indiya ta fara kwashe 'yan kasar ta daga Iran. A ranar 14 ga Maris jirgin saman South African Airways da gwamnatin Afirka ta Kudu ta yi haya ya dawo da' yan Afirka ta Kudu 112.
An gudanar da gwajin likita kafin tashi, kuma an bar 'yan Afirka ta Kudu huɗu waɗanda ke nuna alamun coronavirus a baya don rage haɗarin.
'Yan Afirka ta Kudu ne kawai aka dawo da su da gwajin su ya nuna ba su da lafiya.
Sakamakon gwajin ya tabbatar da cewa dukkan 'yan Afirka ta Kudu, gami da ma'aikatan jirgin sama, matukan jirgi, ma'aikatan otal, 'yan sanda da sojoji da ke cikin aikin jin kai, waɗanda, a matsayin matakin kariya, duk sun kasance a ƙarƙashin lura da keɓewa na tsawon kwanaki 14 a The Ranch Resort.
A ranar 20 ga Maris, Amurka ta fara janye dakarunta daga Iraki saboda annobar.
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, ma'aikatar harkokin wajen kasar Sin ta bayyana cewa kasashe 21 (ciki har da Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad da Tobago, Masar, da Iran) sun aika da taimako ga kasar Sin.
Wasu daliban kasar Sin a jami'o'in Amurka sun hada kai don taimakawa wajen aika taimako zuwa sassan kasar Sin da cutar ta shafa, tare da wani rukuni na hadin gwiwa a yankin Chicago da aka bayar da rahoton sun samu nasarar aika da abin rufe fuska N95 50,000 zuwa asibitoci a lardin Hubei a ranar 30 ga Janairu. Kungiyar agajin jin kai ta Direct Relief, tare da hadin gwiwa da FedEx, ta aika da abin rufe fuska 200,000 tare da sauran kayan kariya na mutum, gami da safar hannu da riguna, ta hanyar jirgin gaggawa zuwa Asibitin Tarayyar Wuhan kafin 30 ga Janairu.
" A ranar 5 ga Fabrairu, Bill da Melinda Gates sun sanar da bayar da gudummawar dala miliyan 100 ga WHO don tallafawa binciken allurar rigakafi da ƙoƙarin magani tare da kare ""al'ummomin da ke cikin haɗari a Afirka da Kudancin Asiya"". "
Interaksyon ta ruwaito cewa gwamnatin China ta ba da gudummawar masks 200,000 ga Philippines a ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, bayan da Sanata Richard Gordon ya aika da masks miliyan 3.16 zuwa Wuhan.
A ranar 19 ga watan Fabrairu, kungiyar agaji ta Singapore ta sanar da cewa za ta aika da tallafin da ya kai dala miliyan 2.26 ga kasar Sin.
Japan ta ba da gudummawar abin rufe fuska miliyan daya ga Wuhan, Turkiyya ta aika da kayan aikin likita, Rasha ta aika da kayayyakin kiwon lafiya sama da tan 13 zuwa Wuhan, Malaysia ta sanar da bayar da gudummawar safar hannu na kiwon lafiya miliyan 18 ga China, Jamus ta ba da kayayyakin kiwon lafiya daban-daban da suka hada da rigunan Hazmat 10,000, kuma Amurka ta ba da gudummawar tan 17.8 na kayayyakin kiwon lafiya ga China kuma ta yi alkawarin karin dala miliyan 100 a matsayin tallafin kudi ga kasashen da cutar ta shafa. Bayan da lamura a China suka bayyana sun daidaita, kasar ta aika da taimako ga kasashe daban-daban da cutar ta shafa.
A watan Maris, China, Cuba da Rasha sun aika da kayayyakin kiwon lafiya da masana don taimakawa Italiya wajen magance annobar coronavirus.
Dan kasuwa Jack Ma ya aika da kayan gwaji miliyan 1.1, da abin rufe fuska miliyan 6, da rigunan kariya 60,000 zuwa Addis Ababa, Habasha don rarraba ta Tarayyar Afirka.
Daga baya ya aika da kayan gwaji 5,000, abin rufe fuska 100,000 da na'urorin numfashi 5 zuwa Panama.
Ma ya kuma bayar da kayayyakin kiwon lafiya ga Kanada. Kasashen Netherlands, Spain, Turkey, Georgia, da Czech Republic sun nuna damuwarsu game da abin rufe fuska da kayan gwajin da aka yi a China.
Misali, Spain ta janye kayan gwajin coronavirus 58,000 da aka yi a China tare da daidaito na kashi 30% kawai, a halin yanzu, Netherlands ta dawo da abin rufe fuska 600,000 na Sinawa waɗanda ke da lahani.
Belgium ta dawo da abin rufe fuska 100,000 da ba za a iya amfani da su ba, wanda ake tsammanin daga China ne, amma a zahiri daga Colombia ne.
A gefe guda kuma, an yi maraba da taimakon da kasar Sin ta bayar a wasu sassan Latin Amurka da Afirka. A ranar 2 ga watan Afrilu, Bankin Duniya ya kaddamar da ayyukan tallafi na gaggawa ga kasashe masu tasowa.
WHO ta yaba da kokarin da hukumomin kasar Sin ke yi wajen sarrafawa da kuma dakile annobar.
"WHO ta lura da bambanci tsakanin barkewar cutar SARS ta 2002 zuwa 2004, inda aka zargi hukumomin China da yin sirri wanda ya hana rigakafi da kokarin hanawa, da rikicin yanzu inda gwamnatin tsakiya ""ta samar da sabuntawa na yau da kullun don kauce wa firgici kafin hutun Sabuwar Shekarar Lunar"". "
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, a matsayin martani ga shawarar hukumomin tsakiya na aiwatar da haramcin zirga-zirga a Wuhan, wakilin WHO Gauden Galea ya lura cewa yayin da "ba lallai ba ne shawarar da WHO ta bayar ba", amma kuma "alamu ne masu mahimmanci na jajircewar hana annobar a wurin da ta fi karkata" kuma ya kira ta "marasa misali a tarihin lafiyar jama'a".A ranar 30 ga Janairu, bayan tabbatar da yaduwar mutum zuwa mutum a wajen China da kuma karuwar adadin masu cutar a wasu ƙasashe, WHO ta ayyana barkewar cutar a matsayin gaggawa ta lafiyar jama'a na damuwa ta duniya (PHEIC), PHEIC na shida tun lokacin da aka fara amfani da matakin a lokacin annobar mura ta 2009. "
Darakta Janar na WHO Tedros Adhanom ya ce PHEIC ya faru ne saboda "hadarin yaduwar duniya, musamman ga ƙasashe masu ƙarancin kuɗi da matsakaitan kuɗi ba tare da ingantaccen tsarin kiwon lafiya ba. "
" A cikin martani ga aiwatar da takunkumin tafiye-tafiye, Tedros ya bayyana cewa ""babu wani dalili na matakan da ke tsoma baki ba dole ba tare da tafiye-tafiye da cinikayya na duniya"" kuma cewa ""WHO ba ta ba da shawarar iyakance kasuwanci da motsi ba""".
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, WHO ta yi kira ga al'ummar duniya don bayar da gudummawar dala miliyan 675 don tallafawa shirye-shiryen dabarun a cikin ƙasashe masu ƙarancin kuɗi, tana mai nuna gaggawa don tallafawa waɗancan ƙasashe waɗanda "ba su da tsarin da za su gano mutanen da suka kamu da cutar, koda kuwa za ta fito".
Tedros ya ci gaba da yin jawabai yana mai cewa ""mu ne kawai masu ƙarfi kamar yadda mafi rauni mu ke"" kuma ya bukaci al'ummar duniya su "zuba jari a yau ko biya ƙarin daga baya"".A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, WHO a cikin taron manema labarai ta kafa COVID-19 a matsayin sunan cutar. "
A wannan ranar, Tedros ya bayyana cewa Sakatare Janar na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya António Guterres ya amince da samar da "ikon dukkan tsarin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a cikin martani".
" An kunna ƙungiyar kula da rikice-rikice ta Majalisar Dinkin Duniya sakamakon haka, wanda ya ba da damar daidaita dukkan amsar Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wanda WHO ta ce zai ba su damar ""mayar da hankali kan amsar kiwon lafiya yayin da sauran hukumomin za su iya ba da ƙwarewar su don ɗaukar tasirin zamantakewar jama'a, tattalin arziki da ci gaban cutar"". "
" A ranar 14 ga watan Fabrairu, an kunna wata ƙungiyar haɗin gwiwa ta WHO tare da China don samar da ƙwararrun ƙasashen duniya da WHO a ƙasa a China don taimakawa cikin kulawar cikin gida da kimantawa ""tsananin cutar da yaduwar cutar"" ta hanyar karɓar bita da tarurruka tare da manyan cibiyoyin matakin ƙasa da gudanar da ziyarar filin don kimantawa ""tasirin ayyukan ba da amsa a matakan lardi da gundumar, gami da birane da yankunan karkara"".A ranar 25 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta bayyana cewa ""duniya ta kamata ta yi ƙarin shiri don yiwuwar annobar coronavirus, "" tana mai cewa duk da cewa har yanzu ba a fara kiran ta annobar ba, ƙasashe duk da haka ya kamata su kasance ""a cikin matakin shiri"". "
" A sakamakon barkewar cutar a Iran, WHO ta aika da tawagar hadin gwiwa don tantance lamarin. A ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, jami'an WHO sun ce za a kara kimanta barazanar coronavirus a matakin duniya daga ""mai girma"" zuwa ""mai girma sosai"", matakin da ya fi dacewa na faɗakarwa da kimanta haɗari. "
Mike Ryan, darektan zartarwa na shirin gaggawa na lafiya na WHO, ya yi gargadi a cikin wata sanarwa cewa ""Wannan gwaji ne na gaskiya ga kowace gwamnati a duniya: Ku farka. "
"Wannan kwayar cutar na iya zuwa kuma kuna buƙatar kasancewa a shirye, "" yana ba da shawarar cewa matakan amsawa daidai na iya taimaka wa duniya kauce wa ""mafi munin shi"". "
Ryan ya ci gaba da bayyana cewa bayanan na yanzu ba su ba jami'an kiwon lafiyar jama'a damar ayyana cutar ta duniya ba, yana mai cewa irin wannan sanarwar na nufin ""muna yarda da cewa kowane dan Adam a doron kasa zai kamu da wannan kwayar cutar""".
A ranar 11 ga Maris, WHO ta ayyana barkewar cutar coronavirus a matsayin annoba.
Darakta Janar ya ce WHO tana "da matukar damuwa da yadda ake yada cutar da kuma yadda take da tsanani, da kuma yadda ake rashin daukar mataki". WHO ta fuskanci zargi mai tsanani saboda yadda ake ganin ba ta kula da cutar yadda ya kamata ba, ciki har da sanarwar gaggawa ta lafiyar jama'a da kuma rarraba kwayar cutar a matsayin annoba. "
