b'Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) enzyme ne wanda ke haɗe da farfajiyar waje (ƙwayoyin sel) na ƙwayoyin cuta a cikin huhu, jijiyoyi, zuciya, koda, da hanji.
ACE2 yana magance aikin enzyme mai canza angiotensin (ACE) ta hanyar rage adadin angiotensin-II da haɓaka Ang ((1-7) yana mai da shi kyakkyawan maƙasudin magani don magance cututtukan zuciya. ACE2 kuma yana aiki a matsayin wurin shiga cikin sel don wasu coronaviruses.
Ana kiran sigar ɗan adam na enzyme da hACE2.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 wani zinc ne mai dauke da metalloenzyme wanda yake a saman endothelial da sauran kwayoyin.
Protein ACE2 ya ƙunshi wani yanki na N-terminal peptidase M2 da kuma yankin C-terminal collectrin na jigilar amino acid.
ACE2 shine furotin membrane mai wucewa guda ɗaya na nau'in I, tare da yankin aikin enzymatically wanda aka fallasa a saman ƙwayoyin cuta a cikin huhu da sauran kyallen takarda.
Ana raba yankin waje na ACE2 daga yankin transmembrane ta wani enzyme da aka sani da sheddase, kuma ana sakin furotin mai narkewa cikin jini kuma a ƙarshe ana fitar dashi cikin fitsari.
ACE2 yana cikin yawancin gabobin: ACE2 yana haɗe da ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin cuta na ƙwayoyin cuta na nau'in II, enterocytes na ƙananan hanji, ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin jini da ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin jini da ƙwayoyin tsoka mai laushi a yawancin gabobin.
Ana kuma samun bayanin mRNA na ACE2 a cikin ƙwayar kwakwalwa, striatum, hypothalamus, da kuma kwakwalwar kwakwalwa.
Babban aikin ACE2 shine yin aiki azaman daidaitawa ga ACE.
ACE yana raba angiotensin I hormone cikin angiotensin II mai ƙuntatawar jini.
ACE2 kuma yana raba carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine daga angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) kuma yana sarrafa shi cikin angiotensin mai fadada jini (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 kuma na iya raba wasu peptides da yawa ciki har da [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, da ghrelin.
ACE2 kuma yana daidaita safarar membrane na mai jigilar amino acid mai tsaka tsaki SLC6A19 kuma an haɗa shi da cutar Hartnup.
A matsayin furotin mai wucewa, ACE2 yana aiki a matsayin babban wurin shiga cikin sel don wasu coronaviruses, gami da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (kwayar cutar da ke haifar da SARS); da SARS-CoV-2 (kwayar cutar da ke haifar da COVID-19).
Musamman, ɗaurewar furotin S1 na SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV2 zuwa yankin enzymatic na ACE2 akan farfajiyar ƙwayoyin cuta yana haifar da endocytosis da sauyawar duka ƙwayoyin cuta da enzyme zuwa cikin endosomes da ke cikin ƙwayoyin cuta.
Wannan tsarin shigarwa yana buƙatar ƙaddamar da furotin S ta hanyar mai karɓar serine protease TMPRSS2, hanawa wanda ke ƙarƙashin bincike a halin yanzu azaman magani mai yuwuwa. Wannan ya sa wasu suka yi zaton cewa rage matakan ACE2, a cikin ƙwayoyin, na iya taimakawa wajen yaƙar kamuwa da cuta.
Koyaya, ƙungiyoyi masu sana'a da ƙungiyoyi masu tsarawa da yawa sun ba da shawarar ci gaba da maganin ACE mai hanawa da ARB.
"Binciken da aka tsara da kuma nazarin binciken da aka buga a ranar 11 ga Yuli, 2012, ya gano cewa ""amfani da masu hana ACE yana da alaƙa da raguwar 34% mai mahimmanci a cikin haɗarin ciwon huhu idan aka kwatanta da sarrafawa. """
"Bugu da kari, ""hadarin ciwon huhu ya ragu a cikin marasa lafiya da aka bi da masu hana ACE waɗanda ke da haɗarin ciwon huhu, musamman waɗanda ke da bugun jini da rashin ƙarfi na zuciya".
